{"tid":1813863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際學者將2019年定為 \"街頭示威者的一年\"","createTime":"2020-01-06T14:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T15:09:23.000Z","uid":153600,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f73bc53de4d5258d2a82e46dcc8fd4320a955b8f","tid":1813863,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:38:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protests_of_2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FProtests_of_2019&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=eb4d7246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protests_of_2019</a><br />\n<br />\n佢哋將拉丁美洲，阿拉伯世界，法國，加泰羅尼亞同香港嘅示威都列為同一類示威<br />\n<br />\n佢哋仲將今年嘅示威浪潮同之前1989年示威浪潮，法國大革命等等相比"},{"pid":"2601449659c75046ddf23b7e1ec254c18b7c040f","tid":1813863,"uid":214997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"The future is young<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5adfbe5b99497eac7e2751dad8c84bca7eab82","tid":1813863,"uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n2019年所發生嘅示威浪潮<br />\n基本上徹底改變世界局勢<br />\n中美關係越趨緊張<br />\n美國同埋伊朗嘅關係亦都越嚟越惡劣<br />\n第三次世界大戰已經如箭在弦<br />\n只係差一個機會，就會爆發"},{"pid":"22b43deafd7a3060bd9bc0483a16e3f3cb3a9c9f","tid":1813863,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"事實權力令人腐化<br />\n<br />\n其實現代人仲需唔需要政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d943ebec794c7ff388cf25ba69620c86b9461100","tid":1813863,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169277c131cbe7c951a0ee9d19db2b96f6873dcb","tid